snippet.title: Paint the Town Red - Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The launch trailer of the Early Access release of Paint the Town Red on Steam. Available October 13, 2015 on Steam.

Paint the Town Red on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/337320

Music - "I Want to Destroy Something Beautiful" by Josh Woodward. Free download: http://joshwoodward.com/song/IWanttoDestroySomethingBeautiful
